title.rendered: HSP Roll R Cover Series 3 Dual Cab Mega Tub – LDV T60 2017+

content.rendered:
The GWM Electric Roll R Cover for the T-60 Range is the ultimate accessory to enhance your vehicle’s potential. Which is why The HSP Roll R Cover is Australias favorite roll top.

With features such a built in LED light, advanced water drainage and the ability to open, close and pause the unit via a touch sensor, your mobile phone or even your factory remote.

excerpt.rendered: HSP Roll R Cover Series 3 Dual Cab Mega Tub – LDV T60 2017+ with Chrome Sports Bars
